Install node by following instructions on http://nodejs.org/

Install npm

  brew install npm

Install express globally

  npm install -g express

change to the app directory and install dependencies
  npm install


run the server
  node app.js

we're using node-mysql to connect to the database
docs at: https://github.com/felixge/node-mysql

using node express for frameworks and templating
http://expressjs.com/
